verses.text:
For thou hadst cast me into the deep, in the midst of the seas;
and the floods compassed  me about: all thy billows and thy waves
passed over me.\f + \fr 2.3  \ft midst: Heb. heart\f*

But I will sacrifice unto thee with the voice of thanksgiving;
I will pay \add that\add* that I have vowed. Salvation \add is\add*
of the \nd LORD\nd*.
